        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks PLS for his generous offer to go over the part on birds [in <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>]. Does not think PLS realises that there are more than 200 pages – most of which will have nothing new for him.</p>  
<p>W. H. Hudson’s proofs have arrived ["Letters on the ornithology of Buenos Ayres", <hi rend="italic">Proc. Zool. Soc. Lond.</hi> (1870): 87–9, 158–60, 332–4, 545–50, 671–3, 748–50, 798–82; (1871): 4–7, 258–62, 326–9].</p> 
